{"tid":806960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【玻璃心軍隊】台軍女上尉遭訓斥 寢室上吊輕生","createTime":"2018-09-05T06:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T16:10:59.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c922b468c1b658de24b32caaee34e6d7617d29ac","tid":806960,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T06:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180905/large/1536125135_32eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180905%2Flarge%2F1536125135_32eb.jpg&h=a2392d04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣陸軍一名陳姓女上尉輔導長，今早遭同事發現在寢室上吊輕生，經立即送台中總醫院急救仍回天乏術。<br />\n<br />\n該名女上尉隸屬駐守台灣中部的第10軍團所屬陸軍機步234旅機步第2營。據內部人事透露，她日前因該單位軍械庫的帳冊有填寫不實的問題，而遭營長抽查發現訓斥。連帶受到處分後，女上尉一時想不開，憤而在寢室上吊輕生。<br />\n<br />\n台灣陸軍拒絕作出評論，僅強調目前全案已移送司法調查，陸軍也會全力配合檢調，以釐清事實。"},{"pid":"7820197e82feeadd245ec7795556ba2cfb405fc8","tid":806960,"uid":3112,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T06:56:40.000Z","msg":"做得軍人都受唔起訓斥同軍法處分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係打起仗黎點算？"},{"pid":"2241d13130746b36344d704e9db3b4d68b27f756","tid":806960,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"7820197e82feeadd245ec7795556ba2cfb405fc8","tid":806960,"uid":3112,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T06:56:40.000Z","msg":"做得軍人都受唔起訓斥同軍法處分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係打起仗黎點算？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T06:58:52.000Z","msg":"兩回事黎 , 打仗會有使命感 , 廢柴都會 heman 上身"},{"pid":"31fce13b74a3f26b68907d42065415f2c3dd9907","tid":806960,"uid":43041,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T07:28:30.000Z","msg":"算好架喇，之前有個比人鬧完，夜晚趁訓教做低曬成個排既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901f9187c7a8f3cc687ccd9c6e32c6def8723020","tid":806960,"uid":49197